===========================================================
| Difference Between Instance Variable and Class Variable |
===========================================================
____________________________________________________________________________________
| Instance Variable              | Class Variable                                  |
| ------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------- |
| Belongs to an object           | Belongs to the class                            |
| Created using `self`           | Created directly inside the class               |
| Separate copy for every object | One shared copy                                 |
| Values can be different        | Same for all objects                            |
| Access using object            | Access using `ClassName.variable` (recommended) |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


